#: ../../Tigase_Admistration/Components/Server_to_Server_Protocol.rst:21
msgid ""
"Normally only one connection to the remote server is required to send "
"XMPP stanza to that server. In some cases however, under a high load, you"
" can get much better throughput and performance if you open multiple "
"connections to the remote server."
msgstr ""

#: ../../Tigase_Admistration/Components/Server_to_Server_Protocol.rst:23
msgid ""
"This is especially true when the remote server works in a cluster mode. "
"Ideally you want to open a connection to each of the cluster nodes on the"
" remote server. This way you can spread the traffic evenly among cluster "
"nodes and improve the performance for s2s connections."
msgstr ""

#: ../../Tigase_Admistration/Components/Server_to_Server_Protocol.rst:25
msgid ""
"Tigase server offers 2 different parameters to tweak the number of "
"concurrent, s2s connections:"
